</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Quote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">Everybody in Katta is Vampyre focused, but the Vampyres themselves are scattered and have hardly any plot of thier own. None of the NPCs care about the three way war between the owlbears, grimlings, and sonic wolves that's happening on thier doorstep. Acrylia Caverns is a big WTF? The cat people don't fit, the akhevans don't fit,</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
